    name: 'Laura G.',
    context: 'Facebook Review',
    quote: 'Picked up our boy just yesterday. He is the sweetest 🥰 very playful, confident (zooms around the house like he always lived here!) and absolutely gorgeous!! I met Sylvia a year ago and always wanted one of her babies, because of how she raises them and how cuddly and well socialised they are. So when the time was right — got one. Highly recommended!!!',
  },
  {
    name: 'Dominika K.',
    context: 'Facebook Review',
    quote: 'Dziękuję za informację ☺️ Profesjonalne podejście, dostałam dużo informacji odnośnie rasy i dbania o te koty. Serdecznie polecam 😁',
  },
  {
    name: 'Zoe T.',
    context: 'Facebook Review',
    quote: '5-star service ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ Fantastic communication, I bought my first Snow Bengal from Sylwia, she was very helpful with care and what they require: healthy kitten, full papers and support. Thank you.',
  },
  {
    name: 'Robert S.',
    context: 'Facebook Review',
    quote: 'Sylwia has been great with us and we are so happy with our beautiful Bengal boys 😃 We were shown all the details of our cats and their lineage and were very confident that we were getting our cats from the right person. Highly recommend Luxury Rosettes 👌',
  },
  {
    name: 'Robert W.',
    context: 'Facebook Review',
    quote: 'Piękne kociaki, profesjonalna hodowla. Polecam wam!',
  },
  {
    name: "Lyla D.",
    context: 'Facebook Review',
    quote: "Sylwia is highly professional and yet extremely loving breeder. In all my years, I've never met such super happy, confident and loving cats. Our Rajeev has settled in so well which is a true testament to Sylwia. I highly recommend her and her bengals. Stunning inside and out xx",
  },
